card.description: Eric Adams assured a nine-member, bipartisan group of New York’s Congressional delegation that he won’t push for a ban on chocolate milk for the moment.
card.title: Eric Adams backs off proposed chocolate milk ban — for now

_source.content:
Thanks to our bipartisan efforts, there is a temporary hold on the decision to ban chocolate milk in schools.

But our fight isn't over.

I will continue to fight for Upstate NY dairy farmers & oppose any effort to replace chocolate milk with vegan juice.

https://nypost.com/2022/04/17/eric-adams-backs-off-proposed-chocolate-milk-ban-for-now/
